{"tid":2060366,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"本港今個月21日將出現日偏食","createTime":"2020-06-11T14:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T08:08:42.000Z","uid":56533,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"99dea03bf6571a37d567d7340f7c5d349fa7f2fc","tid":2060366,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T14:51:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1531475_1_20200611163552.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1531475_1_20200611163552.jpg&h=931fa457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天文台表示，香港本月21日將出現日偏食，由下午2時37分開始，至下午5時25分結束，食甚時間為下午4時08分。<br />\n<br />\n天文台指，這次日食帶橫跨亞洲及非洲，但在香港只能看見日偏食，若天氣情況許可，大部分面向西方而沒有障礙物的地點，都是觀賞日食的理想位置。另外，香港於今次現象中頗接近日食的環食帶，在食甚時，太陽有89%的直徑會受月球阻擋，是自2012年以來香港可觀看的日食現象中食分最高的一次，<span style=\"color: red;\">下次更高食分的日食要待2070年才會出現。</span>而下次能夠在香港觀看的日食將於2023年4月20日出現，屆時的日偏食僅可勉強觀看。<br />\n<br />\n天文台提醒，市民觀看日食時，不應以肉眼或透過望遠鏡直視太陽，較安全的觀測方法是透過針孔，或用望遠鏡把太陽的影像投射在白紙或硬紙板上，然後觀看其投影。市民亦可透過網上直播觀賞是次日食過程。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531475-20200611.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531475-20200611.htm&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0tWqQ%2Br5Wu6dnGlIIIMUdw0%3D&h=1e707a7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531475-20200611.htm&h=28939084\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531475-20200611.htm</a>"},{"pid":"646730f2ec4132c520e6e187c18fdbd9f89a83cc","tid":2060366,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T14:53:39.000Z","msg":"即係有紅月睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c7d6a3f94c2adaa46a18b7de352887168e30c1","tid":2060366,"uid":162046,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"646730f2ec4132c520e6e187c18fdbd9f89a83cc","tid":2060366,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB